column4: NSLOCTEXT("[1951EAF746D022EE46FCF3ABB873AF43]", "2D5811434C58A86F01D82B8700128038", "I am Coelamon, the fish Digimon. Did you come to see me?")

column13: ((16, NSLOCTEXT("[1951EAF746D022EE46FCF3ABB873AF43]", "35480A9E44F69ADEBCD6729C5055F904", "Yes, we looked all over")),(18, NSLOCTEXT("[1951EAF746D022EE46FCF3ABB873AF43]", "51E190CE480EFE9B2F43D18E8B363188", "Now that you mention it")))

column4: NSLOCTEXT("[1951EAF746D022EE46FCF3ABB873AF43]", "583790F748100130E63B90AA80927546", "The bridge upstream is broken and you want to go across. Right?")
NSLOCTEXT("[1951EAF746D022EE46FCF3ABB873AF43]", "D64213264458AF446CD33D82D9AD6A80", "Now, walk on our heads. Don\'t worry.")
NSLOCTEXT("[1951EAF746D022EE46FCF3ABB873AF43]", "40FE3F634F2980BDD344F39881ACACFB", "This world needs more teamwork. Let\'s meet again.")
NSLOCTEXT("[1951EAF746D022EE46FCF3ABB873AF43]", "4272CDB84E33DF91D92DF187D294AC83", "Oh, it\'s you, {Player}. The bridge is fixed.")
NSLOCTEXT("[1951EAF746D022EE46FCF3ABB873AF43]", "0EF6AB9248E1772F6629E3806646F23C", "I got a request. I want you to help me just like I helped you.")
NSLOCTEXT("[1951EAF746D022EE46FCF3ABB873AF43]", "028F109A409778A934896E90A44143C5", "Making a city means saving this island. Everyone will be saved.")
NSLOCTEXT("[1951EAF746D022EE46FCF3ABB873AF43]", "F2BB43B147C1903A699CC3A4D3759F43", "Does that mean you\'ll come to the city?")
